name: What is love?
description:
The answer of AI to this eternal question is in this infinite loop of 10 generative art pieces, here presented with a special frame...

The 10 pieces can be collected individually in my genart account: https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/Barabeke(GenArt)

Who collects at least 10 editions of them will get 1 edition of this (if still in my hands), which I consider the main artwork.
